data.description: Cute and cozy! This home is located in an established neighborhood and makes an absolute perfect home for the first-time buyer. The home has 3 bedrooms; and a bonus room with a private entrance. This additional space makes a perfect office or second living area. Property features mature trees and a storage shed. The lot backs-up onto an open field so there is plenty of privacy. A newroof was installed in late April 2015. This house just hit the market on April 23 and won't last long; Call Gabriel for an appointment at 361-945-LIST(5478).
data.whatILove: This home is very close to the expressway, which makes getting where I am going a snap.
